A technically sound, well-structured empirical analysis paper with a real and timely insight, but the contribution is purely descriptive with no mechanistic account, the main threshold finding is not universal, important KV baselines are missing, and the experimental scale is insufficient to anchor the broad deployment prescriptions the paper claims. Sits at the borderline-reject side of the borderline zone.
