- *Verdict*: Current paper is better than PLORA — bigger scope, more impactful findings.

---

### Dimensional Assessment of the Current Paper

| Dimension | Score | Reasoning |
|---|---|---|
| **Novelty** | Moderate | Scale-dependent inflection point is a genuine insight, but purely descriptive; no theory, no new algorithm |
| **Technical soundness** | Moderate | Threshold inconsistency (Sec 4 vs Sec 5), task-difficulty confound, no statistical testing |
| **Empirical support** | Moderate-High | 1,700 configs, three model families, four benchmarks; but no error bars, no significance testing |
