### Final Judgment:
LDP is a competent engineering contribution with good experimental scaffolding, but it falls short of the ICLR 6.0 acceptance bar. Its incremental novelty, missing statistical rigor, unverified theoretical premise, and brittle "plug-and-play" claims place it below the HiGS/DGPO tier and closer to Jigsaw3D territory. It's stronger than the rejected Jigsaw3D (which had more fundamental methodological issues) but not by a large margin.

